{"tid":791460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲人真係唔知想點","createTime":"2018-08-23T21:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T22:20:58.000Z","uid":202974,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2eec0796fa9439c0402c978ba8e0d3cbf06adfaa","tid":791460,"uid":202974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:34:00.000Z","msg":"比我拆穿咗個大話之後發翻我脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說佢就隱瞞咗自己有2部電話(部電話牽涉到佢其他大話)<br />\n咁咁啱我就係佢書包見到佢另外一部電話，<br />\n我戈陣拎咗出黎望咗一眼，但無睇入面嘅內容就放翻原位。然後就好聲好氣問佢點解要講大話<br />\n佢死口唔應，然後即刻收埋佢另外一部電話(但戈陣我無睇到)佢就叫我搵比佢睇。<br />\n咁我係佢書包搵唔到，佢就係咁鬧我，話我發咩顛，係咪睇錯。<br />\n但最後比我發現佢收咗入佢條底褲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997bae8686a434be03276718b35d12b7266972d9","tid":791460,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:37:40.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"37b893e321f110264ba0dbbf8f975bbb653e5a81","tid":791460,"uid":202974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"997bae8686a434be03276718b35d12b7266972d9","tid":791460,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:37:40.000Z","msg":"1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:38:33.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實在太憤怒"},{"pid":"09a670b9ad51b285822424d6285efdc7fe56f317","tid":791460,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:41:13.000Z","msg":"你係佢第2個 sp 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"66485a7deb25faf9f9bf95873072acd729bd210c","tid":791460,"uid":202974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09a670b9ad51b285822424d6285efdc7fe56f317","tid":791460,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:41:13.000Z","msg":"你係佢第2個 sp 就係咁簡單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:42:45.000Z","msg":"唔係咁㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcddb71a21cc7c7ec42c567d1582f8f1df6721d","tid":791460,"uid":35746,"lik